## 10. Regulatory Alignment

| Regulation / Guidance | Requirement | This Process |
|----------------------|-------------|--------------|
| APP 8 | Reasonable steps before cross-border disclosure | Data location assessment, DPA requirement, overseas tool tracking |
| APP 11 | Reasonable steps to protect PI | Security assessment criteria, Essential Eight alignment |
| AI6 Practice 1 | Understand impacts and plan accordingly | Risk screening and business case requirements |
| AI6 Practice 2 | Decide who is accountable | Tiered approval process with named approvers |
| AI6 Practice 3 | Measure and manage risks | Trial period, ongoing review, decommissioning |
| AI6 Practice 6 | Provide appropriate transparency | Onboarding checklist includes disclosure steps |
| OAIC Oct 2024 | PIA before deploying AI systems | PIA required for Confidential/Restricted data and automated decisions |

